description: THC Farmaceuticals, Inc. owns and operates non-financial institution cash-dispensing automated teller machines at third-party owned retail and commercial locations. The company's machines are placed in hotels, stores, bowling alleys, and other high customer traffic areas for small and medium sized businesses. As of June 30, 2015, it had a total of eight machines for public use along the Wasatch Front in the State of Utah. The company was formerly known as City Media, Inc. and changed its name to THC Farmaceuticals, Inc. in February 2015. THC Farmaceuticals, Inc. was founded in 2008 and is based in Scottsdale, Arizona. THC Farmaceuticals, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Weed Growth Fund, Inc.
